```plantuml
@startuml doitintl_banias

package "Frontend" {
  [Event Reception API] <<Go>> 
  [Event Publisher] <<Go>> 
  [Metrics Exporter] <<Go>> 
}

package "Backend" {
  [Dataflow Pipeline] <<Java>>
  [Schema Manager] <<Java>>
}

[Event Reception API] --> [Event Publisher] : receives events
[Event Publisher] --> [Google Pub/Sub] : publishes events
[Google Pub/Sub] --> [Dataflow Pipeline] : feeds events
[Dataflow Pipeline] --> [BigQuery] : writes data
[Dataflow Pipeline] --> [Error Table] : writes malformed events
[Schema Manager] --> [Google Cloud Storage] : loads schemas

[Metrics Exporter] --> [Prometheus] : exposes metrics

[Event Reception API] --> [Metrics Exporter] : provides metrics

@enduml
```